Lexical::Hints version 0.000002

This module provides a cleaner interface to the built-in "lexical hints
hash" (%^H), and adds some useful additions to the existing mechanism.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

Alternatively, to install with Module::Build, you can use the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install


DEPENDENCIES

None.


